Class PixelContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • in.tamchow.fractal.graphicsutilities.containers.PixelContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    LinearizedPixelContainer 

    public class PixelContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Pannable, java.lang.Comparable<PixelContainer>
    Encapsulates an image or animation frame, for platform independence, takes int32 packed ARGB in hex values as pixels.
